cs.CR, cs.LO, cs.PL, cs.SE, cs.DS 

The paper deals with privacy-enhancing principles and monitoring mechanisms for detecting violations of data minimisation policies in programs. This falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) as well as programming languages (cs.PL) and software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also involves algorithmic analysis and decision-making, which could place it under the category of logic in computer science (cs.LO) or data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
